{"tid":2319903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「暗黑版潤娥」29歲慶生　一坐下曝內在美！美胸遮擋不住","createTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:56:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"11bbcd38e286a9a64f1fffbd77803b9b18c49de2","tid":2319903,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"韓國性感DJ MIU（원미령／譯美玲元）有姣好外貌，與優秀的音樂才華受到許多矚目，因外貌神似網紅企鵝妹及女星潤娥，但由於她不時曬出超惹火辣照，在網上有「暗黑版潤娥」、「暗黑企鵝妹」等稱號。近日由於她生日到來，再度因一張拿蛋糕慶生的照片，意外引爆話題！<br />\n<br />\n身高166公分DJ MIU除了是一名專職DJ之外，也是一名模特兒與知名網紅，累積不少粉絲追蹤，同時經營自己的YouTube頻道，經常拍攝高強度的運動健身影片，對自己也相當嚴苛。<br />\n<br />\n不過因為體態維持過於完美，讓她被酸民攻擊，認為她的腰太不科學，不可能是「純天然」一定動過骨盆手術，或者經過修圖，才能有這樣的身材。然而DJ MIU很「做自己」照樣在ig上分享自己生活日常，近日她po出自己29歲生日的慶生照，又讓一票網友驚豔不已！<br />\n<br />\n只見照片中，DJ MIU捧著一塊四方型的大蛋糕，身穿一件細肩帶的黑色平口連身裙，刻意在生日走氣質路線，然而卻因為坐姿的關係，讓DJ MIU小褲褲似乎不小心走光，令一票粉絲看得臉紅心跳。但這只是「小菜一碟」DJ MIU又上傳了超級深V的連身泳裝，整個胸前幾乎只有薄薄的布遮擋，完美胸型徹底展現在眼前，堪稱是生日對粉絲的大放送，「超凍齡」外貌更讓女粉們紛紛留言直呼：「好羨慕。」"},{"pid":"d21cfab93339f0768edfa4b3accf4d290e8f274b","tid":2319903,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2928587-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2928587-PH.jpg&h=51fe5a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓國性感DJ MIU被稱為「暗黑版潤娥」。（圖／翻攝自2km2km IG）"},{"pid":"134e36b66bc8080edc53ee9511fdb2e7a2b2d85d","tid":2319903,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2928601-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2928601-PH.jpg&h=028d8af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲DJ MIU在29歲慶生照，一坐下小褲褲疑似走光。（圖／翻攝自2km2km IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2928605-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2928605-PH.jpg&h=b254f974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼DJ MIU經常放送超級惹火辣照。（圖／翻攝自2km2km IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2928603-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2928603-PH.jpg&h=5ae13337&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d04e55ccaffd225cabfe00bb4b2b99c5af498f0","tid":2319903,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e540a83fe24e544e6d68560bd7dcc3576e53c946","tid":2319903,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"正....就算改都想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8385bc5eec36a6cd53038a24689cd6e772372831","tid":2319903,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db0b31357ba825fb45e1ca700ecc838212430f3","tid":2319903,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e540a83fe24e544e6d68560bd7dcc3576e53c946","tid":2319903,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"正....就算改都想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"個個你都話正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b624a4d6041ad2add4bdfdfbdf9b7ff8914079a","tid":2319903,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s